title: "What happens if you miss?" (Person of Interest)(1 x 8)
author: Person of Interest Highlights
comment:
"Mr. Reese, I'm highly uncomfortable being here!"
"I'm highly uncomfortable having you here, but I need a spotter."
I always loved the banter between these two.

"I have diplomatic immunity!"
"I'm not a diplomat."
600 yards? Did I hear that correctly? Doesn't seem even close.
